data.description: This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled in a serene neighborhood with meticulously manicured turf grass in both the front and back yards. As you approach, you'll be greeted by the charming curb appeal and a warm, inviting ambiance that beckons you inside. Step through the front door, and you'll find yourself in the heart of the home - the great room. It's a spacious, open-concept living area with a perfect blend of tile and carpet flooring, providing comfort and style. With four well-appointed bedrooms, everyone in the family will have their own space to relax and unwind. The bathrooms are tastefully designed and provide all the comfort and convenience you desire. Pima Butte elementary school is walking distance from your new home.
